data.description: Welcome home in the highly sought after San Mateo neighborhood! This home boasts 3 bedrooms & 1.5 bathrooms, an attached garage (with lots of space), and detached shed in rear! The main living area has a large flex space with direct access to the garage, indoor laundry room, a spacious kitchen and back patio. Covered back patio has lots of room and is perfect for entertaining, with a lovely wooded view! The home is located with walking distance to the park as well as wonderful San Mateo Elementary School. The seller had home inspected and has corrected items in the report. Reports are in document tab. Come take a look & fall in love with this beautiful home!
